headline.print_headline: Isinbayeva Gives Birth to First Child
headline.main: Isinbayeva Gives Birth to First Child

lead_paragraph: Double Olympic pole vault champion and 28-times world record holder Yelena Isinbayeva has given birth to a girl, the Russian Athletics Federation said in a statement on Sunday.
